com.mousebird.maply

Class Point4d

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mousebird.maply.Point4d

  • public class Point4d
extends java.lang.Object
    The Point4d class is your standard x,y,z,w container. The only thing of note here is this is a wrapper for the interal Maply 4D point class.
